{
  "stem": "2906.3",
  "chunk_idx": 10,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 8.0,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 60,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "When you see we coming for a tunnel, go hide someplace.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 60,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Don't sit in the same place where you were sitting.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 60,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "So he did.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 60,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And these-- the-- these men were going around and asking, where is this man?",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 60,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "Where is the Jew?",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 60,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "We can't find him.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 60,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "Where is he?",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 60,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "We can't find him.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 61,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "OK, we get through the tunnel, and he's alive.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 61,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And then, she said let's all sit together, they know, already, that we are, together 29 people and they are Jewish people.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 62,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And then, I said to this-- to who was sitting with us-- I says, you know what?",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 62,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "When the train stops go out, and go to a policeman, and ask him what time it is.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 62,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Don't tell them that they want to kill us.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 62,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Well, maybe he's a killer too.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 62,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "You couldn't trust anybody.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 63,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And he went down, and he went to a policeman asking what time it is.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 63,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "This man ran out from the train, they were running away.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 63,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And we came to-- thank God we made it.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 63,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And then--",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 64,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "We arrived near-- I don't remember.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 64,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "But I know we were in a-- in a headache there.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 64,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "They hold us.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 64,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And then we supposed to go through the Russian soldiers.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 64,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "They told us not to speak Jewish, not to speak Russian.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 65,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "The people who took us-- the-- this was the-- I think the Jewish people who took us there.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 65,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "He told us, don't-- don't say anything.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 65,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "The best thing is to be quiet, because we have to go through the Russia.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 65,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And they-- they wouldn't.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 66,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So, we were there.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 66,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And they came up on the train, and they looked us over.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 66,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And they let us go.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 67,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And so from there, we came to Czechoslovakia.",
      "word_count": 8
    }
  ],
